    <h1>Omnichannel Marketing</h1>
    <p class="description">A strategy that creates a connected, consistent customer experience across every channel — online and offline. Companies with strong omnichannel approaches retain <strong>89% of customers</strong> vs 33% for weak strategies (Aberdeen Group).</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
